properties.content: INSERT INTO tokens     (token, access_token, conversation_id, recipient_id, agency_id, service_type, token_data, expires_at, created_at, updated_at) VALUES (     :#${exchangeProperty.token},     :#${exchangeProperty.accessToken},     CAST(:#${exchangeProperty.conversationId} AS uuid),     CAST(:#${exchangeProperty.recipientId} AS uuid),     CAST(:#${exchangeProperty.agencyId} AS uuid),     :#${exchangeProperty.serviceType},     CAST(:#${exchangeProperty.tokenData} AS json),     CAST(:#${exchangeProperty.expiresAt} AS timestamp),     NOW(),     NOW() ) RETURNING     token
